# Bulk Export Program Members

# Description

Create and execute a bulk export job on program members.

# Project compatibility

Windows | Cross-platform

# Configuration

* 
* Program - Select the program name from the available dropdown list or enter a custom program ID. This field supports String type input.
* Included program member fields - Select the fields from the list to be included in the export file.









* Job info - Automatically generated output variable.
* Export ID - The export ID of the batch job. Automatically generated output variable.
